{"tid":1985772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【新冠肺炎】港大刊於《刺針》研究 推算武漢2月下旬逾23萬人感染","createTime":"2020-04-23T11:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T11:32:42.000Z","uid":301479,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26346955145aaa81a4b90c487d5d03978c384eb9","tid":1985772,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀肺炎（新冠肺炎）疫情持續，目前全球確診個案已超過250萬宗，逾18萬人死亡。港大公共衛生學院世衛傳染病流行病學及控制合作中心研究發現，內地診斷機制或低估確診數字，以截至2月20日數據推算，武漢確診新冠肺炎患者已達23.2萬人，有關研究刊於權威醫學期刊《刺針》。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，研究指內地首個診斷標準在1月15日釐定，當時只將曾到武漢或華南海鮮城、有發燒及肺炎，病毒基因測序與圖譜脗合者，才會列作確診患者。國家衛健委在3日後修改，群組感染、曾接觸有症狀武漢人包括其中，而核糖核酸測試（RT-PCR）呈陽性反應亦是標準之一。論文指出，單是這修改，患者數目已增加7.1倍。<br />\n<br />\n內地之後亦多次修改診斷標準，論文指若內地一早使用第5版標準，即是病人只要到武漢附近地區或爆疫地點、曾接觸到訪武漢的懷疑個案，核糖核酸測試（RT-PCR）呈陽性反應者，估計在2月下旬，內地實有23.2萬名患者，亦由於部分輕微個案無病徵、或未能確診，故相信確實感染數字還不及此。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%8a%e6%96%bc%e3%80%8a%e5%88%ba%e9%87%9d%e3%80%8b%e7%a0%94%e7%a9%b6-%e6%8e%a8%e7%ae%97%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a22%e6%9c%88%e4%b8%8b%e6%97%ac%e9%80%be23%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%ba%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93/ar-BB1340cN?li=AABr7VL&amp;ocid=mailsignout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2588%258a%25e6%2596%25bc%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%2588%25ba%25e9%2587%259d%25e3%2580%258b%25e7%25a0%2594%25e7%25a9%25b6-%25e6%258e%25a8%25e7%25ae%2597%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a22%25e6%259c%2588%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%2597%25ac%25e9%2580%25be23%25e8%2590%25ac%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593%2Far-BB1340cN%3Fli%3DAABr7VL%26ocid%3Dmailsignout&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6iHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=f6007aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%8a%e6%96%bc%e3%80%8a%e5%88%ba%e9%87%9d%e3%80%8b%e7%a0%94%e7%a9%b6-%e6%8e%a8%e7%ae%97%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a22%e6%9c%88%e4%b8%8b%e6%97%ac%e9%80%be23%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%ba%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93/ar-BB1340cN?li=AABr7VL&amp;ocid=mailsignout</a>"},{"pid":"a31026a239834938f56967c39eab3e9b26a426d2","tid":1985772,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832c1420e8538ee977091932d95b181fbe739ed7","tid":1985772,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">相信確診數字還不及此</span><br />\n<br />\n實有人話唔洗你講都知<br />\n但依加係有科學跟據唔係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140d404d470c61adcdc24e501472261983ab43eb","tid":1985772,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"832c1420e8538ee977091932d95b181fbe739ed7","tid":1985772,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">相信確診數字還不及此</span><br />\n<br />\n實有人話唔洗你講都知<br />\n但依加係有科學跟據唔係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">China 9估確診數字</span></div>"}]}